<taxonomicNameLabel box="[416,489,1078,1097]" pageId="54" pageNumber="1264" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
(A) Pereopod 2; (B) pereopod 7; (C) male pleopod 2; (D) pleopod 1; (E) carpal seta of pereopod 7, enlarged; (F) uropod.
</paragraph>
